<span id="xxix-p1"></span>CHAPTER 23.

<span id="xxix.i"></span>

<span id="xxix.i-p1"></span><span id="xxix.i-p1.1"></span>[Genesis
23:1-20](../../../bib/kjv/gen023.htm#001.md)<span id="xxix.i-p1.1"></span>

<span id="xxix.i-p2"></span>**1.** And Sarah was an hundred and seven
