<span id="xxix.i-p39"></span>**19.** Et postea sepelivit Abraham Sarah
uxorem suam in spelunca agri duplici coram Mamre: haec est Hebron in
terra Chenaan.

<span id="xxix.i-p40"></span>**20.** And the field, and the cave that
*is* therein, were made sure unto Abraham for a possession of a
buryingplace by the sons of Heth.

<span id="xxix.i-p41"></span>**20.** Et confirmatus est ager, et
spelunca que erat in eo, ipsi Abraham in haereditatem sepulchri a filiis
